reviewText: One of my elderly mother's favourite programs and now that it no longer screens regularly she is so happy to have some episodes of her own.

See my review for Series 16, no need to repeat here.  LOVE Time Team.  If you have any interest in archaeology, feeling like you are a part of a dig, and have a sense of humor, please take time and watch these folks.  I love them all.
it was new and arrived fast
